<h3>Content Page</h3>
<p><img alt="screenshot of the content boilerplate" height="206" src="Images/web/templates/content-boilerplate.jpg" style="border: 1px solid black; float: right; margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;" title="Content Boilerplate Screenshot" width="400" /></p>
<p>The content page is the most common and versatile page type in our current web builder. This template includes the left navigation with a 710-pixel content area to the right.</p>
<p>Instructions:</p>
<ul>
<li>Download</li>
<li>Open in Text Editor</li>
<li>Scan past minified code to "Begin Copy/Paste" comment</li>
<li>Begin styling!</li>
</ul>
